Loading the PBIX File. 1

We will be loading the Company template  PBIX file(Colaberry Auto Dealership Report 3.PBIX) with a single table (Sales Table)  from Excel Workbook (Shaddy_Outlaw_Sales_Aug.xlsx) loaded to the file.

Steps:

  • Download the PBIX file (Colaberry Auto Dealership Report 3.PBIX) from the above   button.
  • Open Power BI Desktop
  • Select File ->Open -> from the folder where the file is downloaded, select (Colaberry Auto Dealership Report 3.PBIX) file.


Ultimately the final Scatter plot dashboard is supposed to look like the one below.
